      • store

        public void store(RuleKey ruleKey,
         File output)
        Description copied from interface: ArtifactCache
        Store the artifact at path specified by output to cache, such that it can later be fetched using ruleKey as the lookup key. If any internal errors occur, fail silently and continue execution.

        This is a noop if ArtifactCache.isStoreSupported() returns false.

        Specified by:
        store in interface ArtifactCache
